uid":229592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"男人有波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b0cdb0cc708b9cbf997a8629bcb222ee261fa7","tid":1913593,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:17:49.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ed76ebf023bdcb3abee103191884d86b2996a4c","tid":1913593,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7d1f3ad4d8103fa2c9b1cc4eff659e76ca1a8a1","tid":1913593,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"魚仔勁可愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"8bef423d430f1a7d5f75414abf89aa5410380b3c","tid":1913593,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,